  <div class="text-section">
    The Sukkur Division operates <strong>27 stations</strong>, providing <strong>24/7 ticketing and reservation services</strong>. Ticket Vending Machines (TVMs) are installed at <strong>Rohri and Rahimyar Khan</strong>, offering convenient reservation options. All main line stations, as well as major branch line stations, are equipped for <strong>computerized ticketing</strong>, and work is underway to extend this facility to the remaining branch line stations.

    Passengers can also make reservations through the <strong>RABTA mobile app</strong> and the <strong>Pakistan Railways website</strong>, ensuring flexibility and convenience.

    A dedicated <strong>IT server room</strong> at the Sukkur Reservation Office is staffed by IT personnel from <strong>8:00 AM to midnight</strong>, providing technical support for mobile and website users, as well as assisting remote stations with troubleshooting and ticketing issues.
  </div>
